==== Feature additions ====

;<mantis>591</mantis>
<blockquote>DAAP xform was added as a part of the Summer of Code program. This means that you can stream mediafiles from iTunes or mt-daapd</blockquote>
;<mantis>363</mantis>
<blockquote>We have finally imported the Monkeys audio plugin from Ma Xuan. Many thanks to bring more formats to XMMS2</blockquote>
;<mantis>352</mantis>
<blockquote>ID3v1 now have a fallback charset so that you globally configure what the id3 entries is encoded as.</blockquote>
;<mantis>354</mantis>
<blockquote>Clients can now browse serverside directory / files.</blockquote>
;<mantis>942</mantis>
<blockquote>A framework for saving albumart on the server was added and art saved in MP4 and MP3 (id3v2) files are saved in this repo</blockquote>
;<mantis>373</mantis>
<blockquote>We have done a lot of work trying to get LAME encoded MP3's gapless. This is not 100% working yet but the progress is pretty good. Please report how well it works for you.</blockquote>
;<mantis>854</mantis>
<blockquote>The '''radd''' command in the client was moved to the serverside, which means it will be faster and can also act on remote directories.</blockquote>
;<mantis>814</mantis>
<blockquote>The comment field in MP3/FLAC/OGG are now read.</blockquote>
;<mantis>790</mantis>
<blockquote>This changeset unbroke sorting command again.</blockquote>

